;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Arsenal gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Mohamed Elneny th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/mohamed-elneny-58429.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mohamed Elneny</span></strong> c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Basel, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 65 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, nh\u01b0ng anh lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i tr\u00f2n vai khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal gia han hop dong Mohamed Elneny hinh anh\" title=\"Arsenal gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Mohamed Elneny h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vnhttp://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/26/Tien-ve-Mohamed-Elneny-gui-tam-thu-den-fan-nhi-toi-nghiep-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Elneny Elneny</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Wenger s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Xhaka v\u00e0 Ramsey \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n. Mohamed Elneny ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf, anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020 nh\u01b0ng Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Arsenal gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Mohamed Elneny th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Elneny cua Arsenal\" title=\"tien ve Elneny cua Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vnhttp://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/28/khong-the-hieu-duoc-cach-su-dung-elneny-cua-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Elneny g\u1eafn ch\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nGoal kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Elneny v\u1eeba k\u00fd v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal</strong></span> c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ea5y n\u0103m, nh\u01b0ng t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. Daily Mail th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp v\u1eeba k\u00fd v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 3 n\u0103m n\u1eefa, nh\u01b0 v\u1eady Elneny s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Francis Coquelin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Arsenal, vi\u1ec7c Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Elneny c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. S\u1edf d\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n l\u00e0 v\u00ec West Ham v\u00e0 Watford \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 8 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Arsenal gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Mohamed Elneny, West Ham v\u00e0 Watford bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Elneny thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Elneny \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/159675-40942/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Elneny \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"455","checkdouble":"182897"},{"date":"11:28 27/03","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: 6 bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7","type":"","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/27/chuyen-nhuong-mu-6-bom-tan-duoc-gach-do-o-hang-tien-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-col