% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>M\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, khi Mourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m m\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford, nh\u01b0ng Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Michael Carrick s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia v\u00e0o BHL c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Marouane Fellaini, c\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Ander Herrera, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Matic, v\u00e0 anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng Pogba, Herrera hay c\u1ea3 McTominay \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c nhau, v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm (nh\u1eefng) g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 6 bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vnhttp://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><strong>B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</strong></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Italia, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed trinh s\u00e1t theo d\u00f5i Jorginho (Napoli) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 &ldquo;Pogba Serbia&rdquo;. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Jorginho l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa M.U, Liverpool, Arsenal, th\u00ec \u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Savic, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede Ligue 1 (Ph\u00e1p), \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Seri c\u1ee7a Nice, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &ldquo;Xavi ch\u00e2u Phi&rdquo;, v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG. V\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa M.U v\u00e0 si\u00eau c\u00f2 Mino Raiola c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c cho cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 Conte v\u00e0 Pep Gurdiola. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eadt Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 Fred (Shakhtar Donetsk) v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br>\r\n</span></span>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;mso-yfti-tbllook:&#10; 1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"32%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 32.32%; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt;\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:&#10;  0in;margin-